Episode 2: The Intruder 
Aired: September 19, 2005 
Posted: September 21, 2005 
Rating: 8.5/10 
Video: 1920x1080i 
Audio: AC3 2.0 
Synopsis: Earth's battlecruiser Daedalus is infected by a Wraith computer virus. Dr McKay and his team must stop it as members of the Atlantis expedition return from Earth after a meeting at the SGC thanks to the ZPM. During the meeting at the SGC, Dr. Weir learns that the Pentagon plans to replace Major Sheppard with Colonel Caldwell.
